<h1>How to manage Lufthansa Airline flight booking&nbsp; ?</h1>
<p>Managing your booking with Lufthansa Airlines booking , here's a brief guide to help you navigate their booking management system:</p>
<ol>
<li>
<p><strong>Visit the Lufthansa Website:</strong> Start by going to the<a href="http://www.faredealspot.com"> official Lufthansa Airlines website</a>. You can do this through your preferred web browser.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Access the Manage Booking Section:</strong> Look for the "Manage Booking" or "My Booking" option on the website's homepage. This is typically located in the top menu bar.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Enter Your Booking Details:</strong> To access your booking, you will need to provide specific information. Usually, you'll be asked to enter your booking reference or e-ticket number and the last name of the passenger.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Log in (if required):</strong> Lufthansa may also ask you to log in to your account if you have one. This is an added security measure to ensure that only you can access your booking information.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Access Your Booking:</strong> Once you've entered the required details, you should be able to access your booking. Here, you can make various changes and updates to your reservation. These may include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Changing your seat: You can select a different seat if one is available.</li>
<li>Updating passenger information: You can make changes to passenger details.</li>
<li>Adding special services: You can request special services like meals, extra baggage, or assistance.</li>
<li>Changing your flight: Depending on the fare rules, you may be able to change your flight date or time.</li>
<li>Cancelling your booking: If your plans change, you can cancel your booking through this portal.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Follow the On-Screen Instructions:</strong> <a href="https://www.faredealspot.com/flight/lufthansa-airlines/">Lufthansa's Manage Booking</a> system is user-friendly and will guide you through the process step by step. Simply follow the on-screen instructions to make the desired changes to your booking.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Payment (if applicable):</strong> Be prepared to make any necessary payments for changes or additions to your booking. The system will provide you with the cost details, and you can pay securely online.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Confirmation:</strong> Once you've made changes or updates to your booking, you will receive a confirmation email with the revised itinerary.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>Keep in mind that the specific options available in the "Manage Booking" section may vary depending on your booking type, fare class, and the airline's policies. If you encounter any issues or have special requests, you can always contact Lufthansa's customer service for assistance.</p>
<p>Please note that this guide is a general overview of how to manage your booking with Lufthansa Airlines and may be subject to change. For the most accurate and up-to-date information, it's advisable to visit the Lufthansa website directly or contact their customer service for personalized assistance.</p>
